title: Copernicus Proposal - DBC Conference
body:
Idea 
The Copernicus Artwork will be displayed at the yearly conference of the Dutch Blockchain Coalition in the afternoon of the first of July 2021. 

Contribution 
This will grant a lot of attention and publicity amongst the core of the blockchain community in the Netherlands. 

Security 
Maarten will safely bring the Copernicus Artwork by car to the City Theater of Zoetermeer. 

After the conference I propose to be the default holder of the Copernicus Artwork. As long as the artwork is not having a permanent place to reside, the artwork will be stored at my house until further notice. I will safely display the artwork, keep it out off public sight and hand it over as soon as is decided otherwise by the tokenholders.
author: 0x7EE2a944c53fF74d7D686eE80E994dbD40b9dD81
